column5:
bash -c 'case ${REPO_RREV} in
    tiger*)
        git status
    ;;*) printf "\n${REPO_LREV}[%s]\n" "$1 $2"
esac;' - $USER $PWD

column7:
bash -c 'case ${REPO_RREV} in
    ext_adp_s|ext_hero_s)
        git status
        git log -1
    ;;*) printf "\n${REPO_PATH}[%s]\n" "$1 $2"
esac;' - $USER $PWD

bash -c 'case ${REPO_PROJECT} in
    */*/*|*/*/*/*)
          if [[ "${REPO_PATH}" =~ (.*build?)    ]]; then echo "path:[${BASH_REMATCH[1]}]"
        elif [[ "${REPO_PROJECT}" =~ (.*build?) ]]; then echo "project:[${BASH_REMATCH[1]}]"
        fi
    ;;          *)  printf "~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~${REPO_PROJECT}[%s]\n" "$1 $2"
esac' - $USER $PWD
